     <script id="feature-examples-template" type="text/x-mt-template">
        <div class="mt-alternate-translations-examples-container">
            {{examples}}
        </div>
    </script> 
     <script id="feature-lookup-template" type="text/x-mt-template">
        <div class="mt-alternate-translations-lookup-container">
            <div class="mt-alternate-translations-title-container">
                {{title}}
            </div>
            {{parts}}
            <div class="mt-expand-translation-container mt-expand-mobile">
                {{expand-translations}}
            </div>
        </div>
    </script> 
     <script id="examples-template" type="text/x-mt-template">
        <div class="mt-padding-10">            
            <div class="mt-alternate-translations-title-container">Example</div>
            {{examples-valid}}
            {{examples-none}}
        </div>
    </script> 
     <script id="examples-valid-template" type="text/x-mt-template">
        <div class="mt-examples-valid-container">
            <div class="mt-examples-sentences-pairs-container">
                {{examples-sentences-pairs}}
            </div>
            <div class="mt-examples-buttons-container">
                <div class="button mt-example-previous">
                    <div class="leftArrow"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="button mt-example-next ">
                    <div class="rightArrow"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-disclaimer-content-container">               
                <span>These examples are automatically generated using a variety of web resources and cannot be guaranteed as exact or without the inclusion of incorrect or inappropriate language.</span><br/><span><a href="https://aka.ms/translatordictionaryfeedback" target="_blank">Report offensive content</a></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </script> 
     <script id="examples-sentence-pair-template" type="text/x-mt-template">
        <div class="mt-examples-sentence-pair-container mt-hidden">
            <div class="mt-example-source"><span class="mt-italics">{{source-language}}:</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>{{source-prefix}}</span><span class="mt-strong">{{source-term}}</span><span>{{source-suffix}}</span></div>
            <div class="mt-example-target"><span class="mt-italics">{{target-language}}:</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>{{target-prefix}}</span><span class="mt-strong">{{target-term}}</span><span>{{target-suffix}}</span></div>
        </div>
    </script> 
     <script id="examples-none-template" type="text/x-mt-template">
        <div class="mt-examples-none-container">
            <h6>No examples are available for this word</h6>
        </div>
    </script> 
     <script id="expand-translations-template" type="text/x-mt-template">
        <div class="mt-expand-btn mt-expand-more">
            <span class="mt-expand-image"></span>
            <span class="mt-expand-label">{{expansion-label}}</span>
        </div>
    </script> 
     <script id="translation-title-template" type="text/x-mt-template">
        <div class="mt-translations-title">Alternative Translations</div>&nbsp;
        <span class="mt-translations-context">{{translation-context}}</span>
    </script> 
     <script id="parts-template" type="text/x-mt-template">
        <div class="mt-alternate-translations-part">
            {{translations-by-part}}
        </div>
    </script> 
     <script id="pos-template" type="text/x-mt-template">
        <table style="width:100%">
            <tr>
                <td colspan="4">
                    <div class="mt-table-title">{{posTag}}</div>
                </td>
            </tr>
            {{translation_list}}
        </table>
    </script> 
     <script id="translation-template" type="text/x-mt-template">
        <tr>
            <td class="mt-confidence-col">
                <div class="mt-confidence-container {{expand-class}}">
                    <div class="mt-meter-container">
                        <div class="mt-meter-left mt-width-percent-{{leftWidthPercent}} mt-ltr" style=""></div>
                        <div class="mt-meter-right mt-width-percent-{{rightWidthPercent}} mt-ltr" style=""></div>
                        <div class="mt-meter-right mt-width-percent-{{rightWidthPercent}} mt-rtl" style=""></div>
                        <div class="mt-meter-left mt-width-percent-{{leftWidthPercent}} mt-rtl" style=""></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </td>
            {{translation}}
            <td class="mt-back-translation-col">
                <div class="mt-back-translation-container {{expand-class}}">
                    {{back_translations}}
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr><td colspan="4"><div class="mt-spacer-row {{expand-class}}"></div></td></tr>
    </script> 
     <script id="prefix-template" type="text/x-mt-template">
        <td>
            <div class="mt-alternate-translation-prefix-container {{expand-class}}">
                <span>{{prefix-word}}</span>
            </div>
        </td>
        <td>
            <div class="mt-alternate-translation-container mt-margin-adjust {{expand-class}}">
                <div>{{displayTarget}}</div>
            </div>
        </td>
    </script> 
     <script id="no-prefix-template" type="text/x-mt-template">
        <td colspan="2">
            <div class="mt-alternate-translation-container {{expand-class}}">
                <div>{{displayTarget}}</div>
            </div>
        </td>
    </script> 
     <script id="back-translation-last-template" type="text/x-mt-template">
        <span class="{{class-name}}" data-translated-text="{{translated-text}}">{{displayText}}</span>
    </script>

        <span class="{{class-name}}" data-translated-text="{{translated-text}}">{{displayText}}</span>,
